{"tid":2250683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男女涉持刀棍兇人 新城市保安護送","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T13:19:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"21cb8d56ef1eea57878a9b93daa9d8257a4af3f2","tid":2250683,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/XPU5MXSB6NDTJJC732S5VVUCRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FXPU5MXSB6NDTJJC732S5VVUCRE%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEeu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=69c5e61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FXPU5MXSB6NDTJJC732S5VVUCRE%2F&h=9e496149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/XPU5MXSB6NDTJJC732S5VVUCRE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n男女涉持刀棍兇人 新城市保安護送<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3igUP9tku_rUza94z6YZowkeklE=/4194x2359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PBEXLMKHQJHJVCCFZJTSDL32JM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3igUP9tku_rUza94z6YZowkeklE%3D%2F4194x2359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPBEXLMKHQJHJVCCFZJTSDL32JM.jpg&h=a31b3eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告陳美英（左）和黎一龍昨出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田新城市廣場去年9月有大批市民聚集大合唱，一對中年同居男女疑用手機拍攝眾人，與市民發生衝突。其間該對男女涉嫌手持水喉通與長刀恫嚇市民，兩人及後各被票控一項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，案件昨天開審。根據承認案情，女被告警誡下稱：「我嗰陣俾人打，我先拎把刀對峙。」庭上播放新城市廣場閉路電視片段，女被告疑犯案後獲多名保安護送離開。<br />\n<br />\n被告為任職廚師的黎一龍（45歲）及其任職旅遊巴司機的同居女友陳美英（49歲），。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與市民爆衝突<br />\n<br />\n控方庭上播放新城市廣場的閉路電視片段，約晚上10時半，三名商場外判保安員於L3樓層護送女被告離開，其後她獨自乘搭電梯離去。女被告於L1樓層步出電梯，其後於同層推開連接的士站的玻璃門，經的士站朝沙田正街方向離去，身後有一班人緊隨其後。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放網上流傳的片段，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STS1600、1601/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u1O7iuJSid9URLsKKqxSU9b5204=/580x582/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PUBY5DLMSZEEDPUGXIJ227MIVU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu1O7iuJSid9URLsKKqxSU9b5204%3D%2F580x582%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPUBY5DLMSZEEDPUGXIJ227MIVU.gif&h=ed66fafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■圖為兩人當日涉在新城市廣場以刀棍指嚇在商場聚集的市民。"},{"pid":"64fe1f397e746ff024dc980ee3ca463121090706","tid":2250683,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"今次係咪社會服務令算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aac4e7e29b4f3b03e445690c8bca54b94b3d31","tid":2250683,"uid":113250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">49歲</span>女友...果然係真愛。<br />\n<br />\n好一對狗男女。"},{"pid":"df93bf6aff4d90e12bf0d2ad8992cca94eb1a885","tid":2250683,"uid":8170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"咁愛国點會有罪？？"},{"pid":"40f9a376c5915df09f512c8ae38389e6862c7a86","tid":2250683,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81aac4e7e29b4f3b03e445690c8bca54b94b3d31","tid":2250683,"uid":113250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">49歲</span>女友...果然係真愛。<br />\n<br />\n好一對狗男女。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"肥撚到成隻豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a24dc1d2f3afbae9b7f93fb9e14115fc978041","tid":2250683,"uid":155371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T